What you get:
- Live broadcasts of all lectures, where you can ask questions in real time;
- At least 2 new events every month;
- Participation in discussions and the effect of a real scientific club, but without geographical boundaries.

Why Curiosophy?
- Unique topics: things you won't find on YouTube or in open courses;
- Community of like-minded people: thousands of viewers from all over the world united by a thirst for knowledge;
- Format freedom: watch live or later, on your phone or laptop.
